{"tid":1013545,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新城獎棄置橋底　朱明銳促歌手拎獎影相","createTime":"2019-02-08T12:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T05:16:19.000Z","uid":81228,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1a28e5aa80aceb7c422ea55d10613211838234b8","tid":1013545,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208165518899-0208_00862_001_01b.jpg?20190208183832\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208165518899-0208_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20190208183832&h=ae98497a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銳哥好似嬲嬲哋咁！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190208/photo/bkn-20190208165518899-0208_00862_001_02b.jpg?20190208183832\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190208165518899-0208_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20190208183832&h=f686e052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱明銳話歌手們要尊重獎項。<br />\n<br />\n娛圈發生歌手棄獎事件，有歌手將新勁城勁爆獎座丟棄喺橋底！目標人物有羅力威、連詩雅、龍小菌、蔚雨芯同埋吳彤！<br />\n<br />\n前新城電台台長朱明銳接受東網訪問，佢話：「奬項是神聖崇高的，當年以一個獎鼓勵歌手一年的努力！確立歌手的位置及價值！因此，應該珍惜背後的意義！可能有歌手已經退出樂壇，等如有些學生保留大學證書，而不要小學中學證書一樣！尊重與否各自修行！又或者真的家居太小啦！沒有收藏位置，但怎麼也好，理應妥當處理！因為是歌手的曾經光輝奮鬥印記！其實，那五位歌手，現在拿獎座拍一張照片，就是最好的尊重！謝謝」咦，聽落銳哥有啲angry喎，想一齊緝兇喎！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190208/bkn-20190208165518899-0208_00862_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190208%2Fbkn-20190208165518899-0208_00862_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1L7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=8a55fd55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190208/bkn-20190208165518899-0208_00862_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"86eadcfa1c238030c6b5c2f9101ad042171c4af0","tid":1013545,"uid":77948,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"請尊重，謝謝！"},{"pid":"f5432a5f5ef812dcb63fc00b3afe8332e2acd0f0","tid":1013545,"uid":152701,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:14:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾樂壇垃圾人種垃圾奬<br />\n誰他媽的在乎？"},{"pid":"b31f6b86551ce89ea59dfadd4ab9da5316e0c91e","tid":1013545,"uid":37528,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"on9，邊有人會拎舊垃圾黎影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c170a3bb38fa60175b6a2ccd56b69e3b01909f85","tid":1013545,"uid":13638,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會個個都冇"},{"pid":"d9400f0392a6d8eace42292899e0894471b8f38b","tid":1013545,"uid":3093,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"訓導主任咩<br />\n咁大個人仲要聽你支笛做埋啲on9野"},{"pid":"68092584726355e2faed17d48bca87d5a64cb779","tid":1013545,"uid":171594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T14:55:21.000Z","msg":"其實個個丟鳩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad723f71538cfc49772efd8d7e89f88fbae88624","tid":1013545,"uid":211461,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T14:58:19.000Z","msg":"你啲獎係人都有咁cheap咪掉囉<br />\n又唔諗下商台港台TVB唔掉 係掉你個台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3051bb4f58e1eb7fa03ad1f3a10ea830b11e163a","tid":1013545,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"係人都知你新城豬肉獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bde94ffd8fa865f41bb98738d0b65b230b8e2d","tid":1013545,"uid":98289,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"朱生條on9 佬就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20150102/18988337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150102%2F18988337&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1L7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=e5a03141\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150102%2F18988337&h=d65a875a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20150102/18988337</a><br />\n<br />\n缺席勁爆被豎中指<br />\n祖兒寸朱明銳：飲大咗咪受訪<br />\n<br />\n容祖兒前晚到尖沙嘴出席除夕倒數，剛由美國登台返港的她，對於被新城高層朱明銳豎中指捽鼻暗寸缺席上周五的《勁爆》頒獎禮，祖兒句句到肉地回敬銳哥：「我都唔知我咁值得人重視，相信佢當晚飲大咗，我只係覺得如果長輩飲多咗，就唔好做訪問喇，有時飲大咗控制唔到自己，唔通我同長輩計較咩！」<br />\n<br />\n問祖兒會否親自搵銳哥傾？她推搪說：「唔會喇，以銳哥嘅身份，應該係吳雨大哥（英皇CEO）搵佢先至啱。我好尊重銳哥係我前輩，但呢次拉斯維加斯演出真係好難得，以台上滿足感而言，好難用獎座去比較，希望銳哥稍安毋躁。」再問會否向英皇要求度期出席下年度《勁爆》？祖兒竟無面畀說：「都唔會啦，公司安排我做嘢都係深思熟慮，如果獎係值得畀我，自然會畀啦。」"},{"pid":"bf6a0b5dda73c585150bb47399a0e24860c7c5e0","tid":1013545,"uid":191474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86eadcfa1c238030c6b5c2f9101ad042171c4af0","tid":1013545,"uid":77948,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"請尊重，謝謝！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"你來自蒼傲?"},{"pid":"b61085f8e97188e1db5bff1894f53ef1198b138b","tid":1013545,"uid":191474,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"前新城電台台長朱明銳接受東網訪問，佢話：「<span style=\"color: red;\">奬項是神聖崇高的</span>，當年以一個獎鼓勵歌手一年的努力！確立歌手的位置及價值！因此，應該珍惜背後的意義！可能有歌手已經退出樂壇，等如有些學生保留大學證書，而不要小學中學證書一樣！尊重與否各自修行！又或者真的家居太小啦！沒有收藏位置，但怎麼也好，理應妥當處理！因為是歌手的曾經光輝奮鬥印記！其實，那五位歌手，現在拿獎座拍一張照片，就是最好的尊重！謝謝」咦，聽落銳哥有啲angry喎，想一齊緝兇喎！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大部分奬項都係神聖崇高，不過新城咁豬肉，神聖程度就見仁見智啦。"},{"pid":"1f26b254cd42b760a884d4824c8b0a8d3a34a7af","tid":1013545,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54bde94ffd8fa865f41bb98738d0b65b230b8e2d","tid":1013545,"uid":98289,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019